fifty-three & fifty-four
单词
    mild 温和的  It is mild in the fall.   mild food 清淡的食物   spicy food 辛辣的食物
    always 一直
    north       XX is in the north..    XX is in the north of China.
    east
    west
    south  East, West, home is best. 金窝银窝，不如自己的草窝
    news  新闻,消息
    wet 潮湿的， w开头的单词很多都与水有关， water--wash--wine---wave--weep(眼泪)--woman
    season 季节， there are four seasons in the year.
    best adv. 最， adj. 最好的   good/well的最高级   I like green best. 副词在形前动后
    night 夜晚，深夜, 吃完晚饭 at night   evening 指的是刚刚天黑
    rise 升起
    set 落下， 设置
    early adj. 早的   adv. 早地
    late 晚的，晚地
    interesting 有意思的， 有趣的， 令人觉得有趣     the man is interesting.
    subject 话题、科目   we have nine subjects in this term.
    talk 谈话， 比较正式
    conversation 谈话， 比较随意
课文
    an interesting climate 有趣的天气
    what's the weather/climate like in + (月份、季节、地点)   ...天气怎么样
    It is ... in ...   It is dry in west.
    which seasons do you like best?   which are your favorite seasons?
    the nights are short and days are long.   夜短昼长
语法
    频率副词
    never  --  always    从来没有， 一直
    seldom  -- usually   极少, 通常
    often -- sometimes   经常， 有时

    位置： 情系后，实动前
    he always loves her.


fifty-five & fifty-six
单词
    live 不及物， 住，生活     I live in Bejing.
    evil adj. 邪恶的  n.邪恶
    stay  待    stay at the hotel
    home 家
    lunch /lʌntʃ/ 午餐   breakfast, break 打断，打破   fast  快，绝食     supper 晚餐   dinner 正餐，有时也指晚餐    The last supper. 最后的晚餐
    afternoon
    usually
    together adv. 一起  they always come together.
    evening  evening dress 晚礼服    Good evening 晚上好   Good night 晚安
    arrive 不及物，到达    arrive at school    arrive in Beijing    arrive in China   (一般用at， 比较大的用in)


fifty-seven & fifty-eight
单词
    o'clock 点钟   five o'clock  5点整
    shop  商店 规模小的，出售同一类商品的商店       store 大商场
    moment 片刻，瞬间   == wait a second.    at the moment 此时、此刻
课文
    what's the time = what time is it?
    It is .... 的用法
    1.天气    It is very terrible in spring.
    2.时间    It is eight now.
    3.讲电话.   It is Tom.

    the children go to school by car every day.
    on foot. 走路
    by bike. 骑自行车
    by bus.
    by acr.
    by train.
    by air.
    how do you go to school. 如何去上学


fifty-nine & sixty
单词
    envelope 信封， 可数
    writing paper  信纸，不可数名词     a piece of writing paper
    shop assistant 售货员
    size 尺码， 大小
    glue 胶水
    chalk 粉笔     a stick of chalk  条状物
    change 零钱  keep the change 不用找了

sixty-one & six-two
单词
    feel 感觉
    call 叫、请、打电话    Please call the doctor
    doctor
    telephone == phone     call sb.     phone sb.    give sb. a call     give sb a phone
    remember 记得    Do you remember? 你记不记得     I remember.  我记起来了
    mouth 嘴巴
    tongue  舌头     tongue twister 绕口令
    bad 严重的   a bad cold 严重的感冒     the cold color 冷色调

    --ache 疼痛， 长时间疼痛
    headache 头痛
    earache
    toothache
    stomach ache  胃疼
    backache 背疼
    flu 流感    bird flu 禽流感   swine flu 猪流感
    measles 麻疹   have measles
    mumps 腮腺炎
    dentist 牙医
    medicine 不可数， 药
    temperature 温度

    take 表示吃药

课文
    in bed 生病卧床
    in the bed 躺床上睡觉
    what's the matter with him? == what's up?

    So he must stay in bed a week.  错误的
    So he must stay in bed for a week.   for + 段时间， 表示长达

    That's good news for Jimmy.  for对于某人来说

语法
    感观动词  look feel smell sound taste(尝起来)


sixty-three & sixty-four
单词
    better 比较好   good&well的比较级     there is no best, but better.  没有最好，只有更好的。   I am better.我好多了
    certainly 当然， 放在句首句尾表强调     I can certainly help you.     certainly not 当然不可以
    get up 起床     go to sleep/go to bed 起床
    yet adv. 还，仍  常放在句尾
    rich 富有， 油ni
    food   fast food 快餐     sea food 海鲜    green food 绿色食品
    remain 保持

    play 玩    the are playing in the garden.    play with......玩...东西     play with a ball
    match  火柴
    talk big      he always talks big. 他一直讲大话。
    library  图书馆
    drive 开车   drive sb. to sw.
    so adv. 如此地， 程度副词
    quickly adv. == hurry up.
    lean 倾斜，倚靠
    lean out of  身体探出     Don't lean out of the window!  不要探出窗外
    break  打破
    noise 噪音     make a noise  制造
语法
    用动词原型的场景
        1. 情态动词后   he must stay at hone.
        2. be going to后  he is going to do his homework.
        3. 祈使句中   e careful!






